sentences: Wu Xuanyi (born January 26, 1995), is a Chinese singer and actress signed under Starship Entertainment and Yuehua Entertainment.
She is a member of South Korean-Chinese girl group WJSN.
She is also a former member of Chinese girl group Rocket Girls 101 after finishing second in the survival show Produce 101.
Early life ==
Wu was born in Hainan, China.
She joined Yuehua Entertainment, moved to South Korea around 2014 to 2015 and joined Starship Entertainment where she became a trainee.
